    public interface GetElementsOperation<SEED_TYPE,RETURN_TYPE>
extends GetOperation<SEED_TYPE,RETURN_TYPE>
    A GetElementsOperation defines a seeded get operation to be processed on a graph.

    GetElements operations have several flags to determine how to filter Elements.
